    <Fragment slot="subtitle">
      I'm a Microsoft MVP, consultant, and speaker, focused on Dynamics 365 Customer Insights, Copilot, and the Power Platform.
    </Fragment>
  </Hero>

  <!-- Content Widget **************** -->

  <Content
    id="about"
    columns={2}
    items={[
      {
        icon: 'tabler:brand-linkedin',
        callToAction: {
          target: '_blank',
          text: 'LinkedIn',
          href: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/paulinekolde/',
        },
      },
      {
        icon: 'tabler:brand-youtube',
        callToAction: {
          target: '_blank',
          text: 'Youtube',
          href: 'https://www.youtube.com/@paulinekolde',
        },
      },
      
      
    ]}
    image={{
      src: pkOffice,
      alt: 'Pauline Kolde',
      
    }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="content">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-3xl mb-2">My journey</h2>
      <p>
      I entered the world of Dynamics 365 as a career changer in 2017 and quickly found my way into what was then called Dynamics 365 for Marketing, today Customer Insights.
      </p>
      <br />
      <p>
Over the years, it became my focus and I grew with the product and its community. With tech evolving rapidly, especially through AI, I sometimes struggle to keep up, just like many others do.        <br />
        
        <br />
That's why I started my blog in August 2023: a place to share what I discover, test, and learn. “Sharing and caring” might sound cheesy, but it's what shaped my career — and what I hope helps others, too.      </p>
      <br />
      <p>Curious to dive deeper? Follow along here.</p>
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="bg">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-transparent"></div>
    </Fragment>
  </Content>

