        description: `Together with Benedikt Bergmann and Björn Zahnow, I'm building up the German branch of CRMK bringing the spirit and values of our Swedish colleagues to a new market.<br /> At CRMK, we work with curiosity, collaboration, and transparency, always aiming for sustainable, human-centered growth. <br /> It's not just about delivering great solutions in Dynamics 365 Customer Insights, Copilot, and the Power Platform, it's about creating an environment where people enjoy their work, share knowledge openly, and build long-term value for clients and community. <br /> `,
        icon: 'tabler:briefcase',
      },
      {
        title:
          'Manager <br /> <span class="font-normal">Cluster Dynamics Reply, Hamburg</span> <br /> <span class="text-sm font-normal">April 2021 - October, 2025</span>',
        description: `I lead the Customer Insights team, shaping strategy, mentoring colleagues, and exploring new ideas in customer data.<br /> I loved inspiring clients in pre-sales by showing what's possible with the Microsoft stack and sparking fresh ideas. <br /> Together with my clients, I designed tailored, data-driven solutions that make marketing and CRM smarter and more personal`,
        icon: 'tabler:briefcase',
      },
      {
        title:
          'CRM Consultant <br /> <span class="font-normal">Fellowmind, Eschborn</span> <br /> <span class="text-sm font-normal">September 2017 - March, 2021</span>',
        description: `One of the best decisions I ever made was joining the Young Talent Program at CRM Partners (now Fellowmind).<br /> As a career changer, it opened the door to Microsoft, Dynamics 365, and the Power Platform and taught me not just the tech, but problem-solving, creativity, and how technology can transform businesses.<br /> Looking back, I wouldn't change a thing. It was the start of an exciting journey.`,
        icon: 'tabler:briefcase',
      },
    ]}
    classes={{ container: 'max-w-3xl' }}
  />
